title: Sweeney Todd The Demon Barber Of Fleet Street 2007 BRRip
description:
===================================================================================
In the Victorian London| the barber Benjamin Barker is married to the gorgeous Lucy and they have a lovely child| Johanna. The beauty of Lucy attracts the attention
of the corrupt Judge Turpin| who falsely accuses the barber of a crime that he did not commit and abuses Lucy later after gaining custody of her. After fifteen years
in exile| Benjamin returns to London under the new identity of Sweeney Todd| seeking revenge against Turpin. He meets the widow Mrs. Lovett who is the owner of a
meat pie shop who tells him that Lucy swallowed arsenic many years ago| and Turpin assigned himself tutor of Johanna. He opens a barber shop above her store|
initiating a crime rampage against those who made him suffer and lose his beloved family.
